func (c context.Context) Done() <-chan struct{}
Returns a channel that is closed when work associated with this
context should be canceled.

func (c context.Context) Deadline() (dl time.Time, ok bool)
Returns the time when work associated with this context should be canceled;
ok is false if there is no deadline.

func (c context.Context) Err() error
If context is not yet closed, returns nil; if context is closed,
returns error explaining why.

func (c context.Context) Value(key interface{}) interface{}
Returns a value associated with the context with a specific key.

Useful for request-scoped data.
